<p>Welcome <%= @resource.name %>!</p>

<p>An account has been created for you at the SSP Information Center. This account will make it easier for you to
  manage your interaction with SSP. This is meant for your convenience, but not as a replacement for picking up the
  phone and calling us when you need to.</p>

<p>To use the account, you will log on using your email address (to which this email has been sent, as well as a password.
When you activate your account by clicking on the link below, you'll be prompted to set a password. Please call the office if
you encounter any difficulty in getting logged in.</p>
<p>After activating your account, be sure to bookmark your MySSP page. The link below becomes inactive after it has been used.</p>
<p>To start using the Information Center, please click on the link below now.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Confirm my account', confirmation_url(@resource, :confirmation_token => @resource.confirmation_token) %></p>

